              MVPY/NTSE/Olympiad Exam (ii) 2 Yrs program for XI-XII CBSE + NEET/IIT-JEE. Entrance
              Exams. Free Fast Track Revision for Science, Maths & Mental Ability to class VIII, IX
              & X if students Register for further program in Takshila Certificate of Merit for
              students who scoring 80% & above with medals.. Certificate of participants for all
              Students. Takshila provides complete Study Material,Test Series,Mock Test and coaching
              for school syllabus & All Competitive Exam.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Features Section -->
