            <h2 class="text-primary">Salient Features</h2>
            <ul class="list-group">
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Eligibility: </strong>Students studying in Class VIII, IX, X & XI
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Dates of Exam: </strong>24 Dec 2023 & 21 Jan 2024
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Mode of Examination: </strong>Offline</li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>No. of Question / Subject: </strong>Total 50 Questions: Science 20: Maths 20
