              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>No. of Question / Subject: </strong>Total 60 Questions: Physics 15,
                Chemistry 15, Maths/ Biology 15 & Reasoning 15 for class XI.
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Syllabus: </strong>CBSE syllabus of Science, Mathematics of respective
                classes and IQ comprises of questions on Logical & Mental Ability For class VIII to
                X and Physics, Chemistry, Mathematics /Biology and Reasoning for Class XI.
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Pattern of Question: </strong>Objective Type Questions 4 choices (Single
                correct answer).(Sample test papers are available at
                website:www.takshilainstitute.in
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Marking Scheme: </strong>For Class VIII to X Max. Marks : 200 (+ 4 for
                correct answer) (No Negative Marking for wrong answer).
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Medium of Exam: </strong>For Class XI Max. Marks : 120 (+ 2 for correct
                answer) (No Negative Marking for wrong answer).
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Medium of Exam: </strong>English Only</li>
              <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Duration of Exam: </strong>1 Hr.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Fee: </strong>Rs. 300/-</li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Results: </strong>Contact the nearest Takshila Institute
